&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About us.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Trumid is a dynamic fintech revolutionizing the landscape of fixed income trading. With intelligent, easy-to-use, electronic solutions, we are rapidly growing and seeking exceptional talent to help redefine the boundaries of technology and finance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Founded in 2014 by a team of fixed income market experts, Trumid has quickly become one of the top three corporate bond e-trading platforms in the U.S. Today, over 1,300 traders from an extensive and expanding client network of 890+ buy-and sell-side institutions transact on Trumid monthly.&lt;/p&gt;
