&lt;li&gt;Curated data models in BigQuery using dbt that define consistent business metrics across Trumid&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Data delivery systems that support dashboards, client-facing reporting, compliance datasets, and other external data products&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Governed datasets and documentation that enable self-service analytics across the organization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
